OL,3,CHouthis vow to escalate against UK and
OL,4,CUS, in rare interview with Western
OL,5,Cmedia
OL,7,FA Houthi official warned of escalation
OL,8,Fagainst the UK and US, in one of the
OL,9,Ffirst in-depth interviews the Yemen-
OL,10,Fbased, Iran-backed group has given
OL,11,Fsince the Gaza war, as Global Security
OL,12,FEditor Rohit Kachroo reports.
OL,14,FThe Houthis have vowed to continue
OL,15,Fattacks on UK and US ships in the Red
OL,16,FSea if there is no ceasefire in Gaza,
OL,17,Fand told ITV News it would attack the
OL,18,FUK itself if it had the capacity to do
OL,19,Fso.
