OL,3,CHouthis vow to escalate against UK and
OL,4,CUS, in rare interview with Western
OL,5,Cmedia
OL,7,FIn the first in-depth interview given
OL,8,Fto Western media by the Iranian-backed
OL,9,FYemeni group since the October 7 Hamas
OL,10,Fattacks in Israel, a Houthi official
OL,11,Fsaid it will target the UK and the US
OL,12,F"wherever" it can reach.
OL,14,F"If we had rockets and warplanes that
OL,15,Fcould reach deep into America and
OL,16,FBritain, we would hit them without any
OL,17,Fhesitation, as long as they are
OL,18,Fattacking Yemen", Mohammed al-Bukhaiti
OL,19,F- a spokesperson and official - told
OL,20,FITV News Global Security Editor Rohit
OL,21,FKachroo.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.!/*%/"-$ /*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,
