OL,3,CHouthis vow to escalate against UK and
OL,4,CUS, in rare interview with Western
OL,5,Cmedia
OL,7,F"This is a legitimate right for
OL,8,FYemen", he added.
OL,10,F'If we had rockets and warplanes that
OL,11,Fcould reach deep into the US and UK,
OL,12,Fof course we would hit them', Houthi
OL,13,Fofficial Mohammad al-Bukhaiti told ITV
OL,14,FNews Global Security Editor Rohit
OL,15,FKachroo.
OL,17,FThe Houthi official said the group
OL,18,Fwould escalate if Israeli action in
OL,19,FGaza continues with what it perceives
OL,20,Fas Western support.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/9
