OL,3,CHouthis vow to escalate against UK and
OL,4,CUS, in rare interview with Western
OL,5,Cmedia
OL,7,FHe said that if aggression against
OL,8,FGaza does not stop and if the "siege
OL,9,Fis not lifted" there will be an
OL,10,F"escalation" which will be "announced
OL,11,Fin due course", Mr al-Bukhaiti said.
OL,12,FHe added that the Houthis have "many
OL,13,Foptions" in terms of escalation, if
OL,14,Fthe UK and US were to "target Yemeni
OL,15,Fcivilians".
OL,17,F"Our war (attacks against US and UK
OL,18,Fvessels) is a legitimate one", he
OL,19,Fsaid, speaking from within Yemen.
