OL,5,Cmedia
OL,7,F"We did not initiate attacks on
OL,8,FAmerica or Britain either in the Red
OL,9,FSea or in their countries, but if
OL,10,Fthere is aggression against us from
OL,11,Fany country we will respond wherever
OL,12,Four hands can reach", he added.
OL,14,FMr al-Bukhaiti didn't rule out
OL,15,Ftargeting British and American
OL,16,Fembassies and army bases, when asked
OL,17,Fby ITV News.
