OL,3,CHouthis vow to escalate against UK and
OL,4,CUS, in rare interview with Western
OL,5,Cmedia
OL,7,FThe Houthis are a Shia Islamist
OL,8,Fpolitical and military group - backed
OL,9,Fby Iran - that has been fighting a war
OL,10,Fagainst Yemen's government - which is
OL,11,Fsupported by Saudi Arabia - since 2014.
OL,13,FThe first Houthi attack on commercial
OL,14,Fships in the Red Sea came on 19th
OL,15,FNovember. The group has since attacked
OL,16,Fmore than 20 ships using missiles and
OL,17,Fdrones. The attacks have been in
OL,18,Fresponse to the war in Gaza.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/9
