OL,5,Cmedia
OL,7,FThe Houthis have said they will target
OL,8,Fall ships bound for Israel or vessels
OL,9,Fthat are Israeli-owned or flagged. UK
OL,10,Fand US-flagged and owned ships have
OL,11,Falso been targeted.
OL,13,FSome shipping companies have stopped
OL,14,Fusing the Red Sea - which is used as a
OL,15,Froute by 15% of global sea trade - as
OL,16,Fa result of the attacks.
OL,18,FThe UK and US have retaliated with air
OL,19,Fstrikes in response to Houthi attacks
OL,20,Fin the Red Sea.
